{"tid":427153,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你知道你哋唔啱對方","createTime":"2017-10-07T09:26:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T16:42:16.000Z","uid":431,"like":138,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"0355054e3dcb17bc22877c79101005202603d2bf","tid":427153,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T09:26:06.000Z","msg":"你望住佢 你知道你好愛佢<br />\n你都知道你地唔會行到去最後<br />\n有啲野你一早feel到 你同自己講只係需要時間去磨合<br />\n磨合左咁多次 你意識到其實你地唔適合對方<br />\n無論你地幾愛對方都好<br />\n你地太唔同 而你只能夠妥協 只能夠接受 你好難受<br />\n每一次都消耗緊你地之間嘅感情<br />\n感情同耐性總有一日會消耗完<br />\n你大概想像得到嗰一日會係點<br />\n你會決定走 決定唔再放希望係依段感情上面<br />\n佢可能會挽留你 但係你心入面知道你地冇將來<br />\n佢拍一拍你 問你做咩發吽逗啊<br />\n你無講野 你攬住佢 希望依一日唔好咁快嚟到"},{"pid":"efb6c657dc0f0cd03f65ed2d47f8afa28b5f05de","tid":427153,"uid":4679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T09:43:26.000Z","msg":"頑石哪天變黃金 我可以等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38d5a7f088167f9fd60a5b6e7531219502e4383","tid":427153,"uid":15473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T09:55:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/offtopic.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cc2235cf7a3be2b5550c8f3a8fef0d861507be1","tid":427153,"uid":29485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T09:56:49.000Z","msg":"又loop"},{"pid":"1d21a053dc554c00f89ba75a615ec7d73f7c2baa","tid":427153,"uid":144913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T10:44:56.000Z","msg":"啱呀"},{"pid":"ca57dc19a5037c9448564453898a3cadc071abee","tid":427153,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T11:21:49.000Z","msg":"難道我存在是為了你"},{"pid":"f35570bfb4b42c8403470483a1c831be59b9c2f8","tid":427153,"uid":15473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T11:24:50.000Z","msg":"收聲"},{"pid":"45e2100662963b45121fe048cae9818294134c87","tid":427153,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T11:35:01.000Z","msg":"